@@ -95,6 +95,22 @@ Clone a missing plugin.
 %
 ```
 
+Git wrappers may write progress to stdout even when passed `--quiet`. Keep that
+output out of the generated script without hiding it from the user.
+
+```zsh
+% function git { [[ $1 == clone ]] && print 'wrapper: cloning repository'; mockgit "$@" }
+% antidote-script fakeuser/fakerepo >$T_TEMPDIR/generated.zsh 2>$T_TEMPDIR/diagnostics
+% cat $T_TEMPDIR/generated.zsh | subenv ANTIDOTE_HOME
+fpath+=( "$ANTIDOTE_HOME/fakeuser/fakerepo" )
+source "$ANTIDOTE_HOME/fakeuser/fakerepo/fakerepo.plugin.zsh"
+% cat $T_TEMPDIR/diagnostics
+# antidote cloning fakeuser/fakerepo...
+wrapper: cloning repository
+% function git { mockgit "$@" }
+%
+```
